      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777140103,
      "updated": 1777140103
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed017f0000000000c9243c",
      "text": "[さもありなん]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777140095,
      "updated": 1777140103
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed017e0000000000c9243b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777140094,
      "updated": 1777140094
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed018a0000000000c9243e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777140106,
      "updated": 1777140106
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed000d000000000070f2dc",
      "text": "そうでないのに、まるでそうなっているかのように",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777139725,
      "updated": 1777139828
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed0bca000000000070f326",
      "text": " 「さも〇〇かのように」で使うときの「さも」",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777142731,
      "updated": 1777142817
    },
    {
      "id": "69ecfffd000000000070f2d9",
      "text": " [あたかも]と同じ意味",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777139709,
      "updated": 1777139724
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed0002000000000070f2db",
      "text": " この意味がWeblio辞書に載ってなかった [vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777139715,
      "updated": 1777139895
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed0087000000000070f2e0",
      "text": "  https://www.weblio.jp/content/さも",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777139848,
      "updated": 1777139848
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed01910000000000c9243f",
      "text": "  もしかして私[vlzs.icon]の誤用で、多くの人が共有してる意味でない?",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777140113,
      "updated": 1777142759
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed0088000000000070f2e1",
      "text": " 井戸端で使用されている様子",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777139848,
      "updated": 1777140018
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed013f0000000000c92433",
      "text": "  > [vlzs.icon] ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777140031,
      "updated": 1777140031
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed013f0000000000c92434",
      "text": "  >  座って作業をしてたらドキドキしてきたので運動する",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777140031,
      "updated": 1777140031
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed013f0000000000c92435",
      "text": "  >   心拍数が早くなってる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777140031,
      "updated": 1777140031
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed013f0000000000c92436",
      "text": "  >   ステッパーを踏んで楽になろう",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777140031,
      "updated": 1777140031
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed013f0000000000c92437",
      "text": "  > (...)",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777140031,
      "updated": 1777142818
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed013f0000000000c92438",
      "text": "  >  さも休憩中に毎日やってるかのように書いたがその用途ではあまりやったことがなかったな",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777140031,
      "updated": 1777140031
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed013f0000000000c92439",
      "text": "   from [2026/04/24#69eb803300000000007dee19]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777140031,
      "updated": 1777140039
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed0092000000000070f2e5",
      "text": "  > [inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777139858,
      "updated": 1777139861
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed0096000000000070f2e6",
      "text": "  > (...)",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777139862,
      "updated": 1777139870
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed008d000000000070f2e2",
      "text": "  >  今の自分の性格・性質と幼少期の弟との関係性の話をAIにすると、さも因果関係があるような返答をしてくるが、そこから客観的見てとか、因果関係そんなにあるかな？と聞くと、急にトーンが低くなるやつ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777139853,
      "updated": 1777139855
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed008f000000000070f2e3",
      "text": "  >   気にせず前半で話を終えてると自分の思い込みを強化するだけになってしまう",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777139855,
      "updated": 1777139855
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed008f000000000070f2e4",
      "text": "  >   ひとり[エコーチェンバー現象]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777139855,
      "updated": 1777139855
    },
    {
      "id": "69ed0074000000000070f2df",
      "text": "   from [2026/04/25#69eca99a00000000009646eb]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777139829,
      "updated": 1777139892
    },
